From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 5 Mar 2026 23:13:02 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add UDP tracker support
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Implements UDP tracker protocol (BEP 15):
- Supports both HTTP and UDP tracker URLs
- Automatically detects tracker type from URI scheme
- Implements connect and announce requests for UDP
- Binary packet encoding/decoding for UDP protocol
- Falls back to HTTP for non-UDP trackers

No new dependencies required - uses Lwt_unix for UDP sockets.

🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)

Co-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
